ber  in  stance posted a  employee increase from the previous year reaching  employees at its san clemente headquarters stance was listed no  on the orange county business journal’s list of the  biggest based in orange county apparel businessescitation needed sponsorshipedit stance’s brand ambassadors are called punks and poets they include musicians athletes designers artists stylists writers and photographers athletes andre drummond allen iverson chandler parsons dwyane wade klay thompson lauren fleshman todd richards kassia meador john john florence silje norendal nyjah huston chris cole theotis beasley andrew reynolds kenny roczen chad reed troy lee bubba watson mikey wright musiciansbands soko haim nikki lane thurzday santigold rihanna  big sean willow smith models bambi northwoodblyth hanne gaby odiele designers and stylists imogene barron ronnie fieg alexandra spencerth  bleeker artistsillustratorsphotographers brooke reidt josie ramondetta langley fox hemmingway mark oblow russ pope kid creature todd francis referencesedit    how stance socks innovative approach led to its nba deal sneakershoutscom  retrieved    crunchbase stance crunchbasecom retrieved    luxurysocks startup stance raises m to expand into underwear wall street journal  retrieved    a b dimartino mediha  sock maker raises m orange county business journal retrieved    stance valued at m with m series d pitchbook  retrieved    nba agrees licensing deal with stance socks as league official sock espn    stance signs deal with mlb to be official sock provider espn    httpwwwsanclementetimescombusinessbeatstancelocksoriginalcontractwithnba  httpblogswsjcomventurecapitalluxurysocksstartupstanceraisesmtoexpandintounderwear  httpswwwstancecomabout  httpwwwmensjournalcomstylecollectionstancesocksaddsitslogotothenbauniform  httpswwwstancecompunksandpoets  rihanna teams up with stance for sock collection ballerstatuscom july    external linksedit official website retrieved from httpsenwikipediaorgwindex